Package logic

Class Notification

java.lang.Object
logic.Notification
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Notification extends Object implements Serializable
The Notification class represents a notification related to an order in the park management system. It contains information such as park name, order number, visitor ID, date, time, and number of visitors.
